edBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:21:30.000Z","msg":"繼太空站後又多一件垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【失控衛星】中國天宮一號殘骸　預期2018年墜入歐洲 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=28755\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D28755&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=785fc48f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=28755</a>"},{"pid":"07234d9ffd1855c5254078f19d891bdbb3997305","tid":532180,"uid":61830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7212b95edf85039704ea5c1353d375ccff489600","tid":532180,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:54:39.000Z","msg":"其實我一路都想問...想清左太空垃圾點解唔將D垃圾向太陽果個方向推一推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:29:11.000Z","msg":"先唔講去唔去到太陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n脫離地球軌道唔係咁易，相信堆返d垃圾返地球一定用細力好多。<br />\n<br />\nd垃圾已經係低軌道，舊野就要放係比低軌道更低既地方，但需要既動力就要大好多先可以唔會飛返落地球。<br />\n一係就地對太空，但更加哂錢。"},{"pid":"d4a96a1cd15ccfeb97dfede4291e27a1d60611ca","tid":532180,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"整粒死亡星出黎 <br />\n不過支那又點會整到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8248729042d2ee33c54cc002134ee6bdda00710a","tid":532180,"uid":170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"首都有咁多懸浮粒子不難理解"},{"pid":"ad71ff83e16fa529f64255c7c0a9b7fa72837301","tid":532180,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:34:45.000Z","msg":"Article IV<br />\nStates Parties to the Treaty undertake not to place in orbit around the earth any objects carrying nuclear weapons or any other kinds of weapons of mass destruction, install such weapons on celestial bodies, or station such weapons in outer space in any other manner.<br />\n<br />\nThe moon and other celestial bodies shall be used by all States Parties to the Treaty exclusively for peaceful purposes. The establishment of military bases, installations and fortifications, the testing of any type of weapons and the conduct of military manoeuvres on celestial bodies shall be forbidden. The use of military personnel for scientific research or for any other peaceful purposes shall not be prohibited. The use of any equipment or facility necessary for peaceful exploration of the moon and other celestial bodies shall also not be prohibited.<br />\n<br />\n呢一段簡單嚟講就係話任何國家都唔可以喺太空度放WMD<br />\n但傳統武器係冇bam到<br />\n即係美佬如果玩kinetic bombardment佢理論上應該係冇違約<br />\n但美佬都唔會咁明目張膽<br />\n<br />\n支那佬而家咁撚大聲同人講自己想放碌激光砲上太空同打開口牌有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上面有人提到個垃圾自宮一號<br />\nOuter Space Treaty嘅Article VII好似關事<br />\n<br />\nArticle VII<br />\nEach State Party to the Treaty that launches or procures the launching of an object into outer space, including the moon and other celestial bodies, and each State Party from whose territory or facility an object is launched, is internationally liable for damage to another State Party to the Treaty or to its natural or juridical persons by such object or its component parts on the Earth, in air space or in outer space, including the moon and other celestial bodies.<br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係簽署國係需要為佢發射去太空嘅物品對太空、地球嘅天空、<span style=\"color: red;\">另一個簽署國</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">另一個簽署國嘅natural or juridical persons</span>所造成嘅損壞負責，就算係跌粒螺絲整親人都要負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那係有份簽<br />\n美佬 俄佬都有簽<br />\n我就想睇下到時真係跌去第二個國家支那會點spin"},{"pid":"348083fbbe56817b5650ea9bab837bb358bbd9fa","tid":532180,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4b62b4e0dd7435f1363e0a70ffdccdbfe5a5810","tid":532180,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6249110d7764eec1ecdba7df746535fcc2612f8f","tid":532180,"uid":42982,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/231823_90bec3e5c23ed8fae214ca4012f155cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F231823_90bec3e5c23ed8fae214ca4012f155cf.png&h=4f068baf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"This battlestation is fully operational"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:36:01.000Z","msg":"呢件垃圾係咪未用就爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}